1380
01:40:15,276 --> 01:40:17,577
No. Yet another thing
I don't know.

1381
01:40:17,579 --> 01:40:19,412
<i>Well, polyphony is</i>

1382
01:40:19,414 --> 01:40:21,180
<i>from the middle ages.</i>

1383
01:40:21,182 --> 01:40:23,716
