with the left hand...

1418
01:42:26,540 --> 01:42:29,108
The first voice played
with the right hand.

1419
01:42:29,110 --> 01:42:32,378
<i>That is called</i> cantus firmus
<i>or "can-toos feer-mus."</i>

1420
01:42:32,380 --> 01:42:35,982
And together, these three
